            <a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/fr/firefox/addon/localcdn-fork-of-decentraleyes" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><img src="assets/images/get-firefox-add-on.png" alt="Get uBlock Origin for Firefox"></a>
